Apply a unified background to the footer
Add this to your custom CSS (loaded last):

css
footer.footer {
    background-color: #f2f2f2 !important; /* same light grey as menu */
    color: #000 !important;               /* ensure readable text */
    padding: 10px 0;
}
If you want the inner container to match too:

css
.footer-container {
    background-color: #f2f2f2 !important;
}
